    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜入《声纳侦察员》的水下世界，驾驶一艘孤独的潜艇，探索深海以激活失落的信标，恢复与遗忘文明的联系。   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137740/extras/c34026a44ff1c26db93b3df417441a42.poster.avif?t=1733692165\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137740/extras/c34026a44ff1c26db93b3df417441a42.webm?t=1733692165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137740/extras/c34026a44ff1c26db93b3df417441a42.mp4?t=1733692165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的导航能力和记忆地形的能力将是生存的关键。小心，你并不孤单，敏捷的反应可能会拯救你脱离下方的危险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137740/extras/647f8d5432161c1f6cb523b5d36d259e.poster.avif?t=1733692165\" width=600 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137740/extras/647f8d5432161c1f6cb523b5d36d259e.webm?t=1733692165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137740/extras/647f8d5432161c1f6cb523b5d36d259e.mp4?t=1733692165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索新环境时，你将解锁具有独特能力的新潜艇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137740/extras/13eeaee5e9412b3e3b86e326d623334a.poster.avif?t=1733692165\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137740/extras/13eeaee5e9412b3e3b86e326d623334a.webm?t=1733692165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137740/extras/13eeaee5e9412b3e3b86e326d623334a.mp4?t=1733692165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你认为能比朋友们更快掌握深海吗？在排行榜上骄傲地展示你的成绩，并挑战他们来证明你错了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137740/extras/f02345333a681606799033c4cc1cfa34.poster.avif?t=1733692165\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137740/extras/f02345333a681606799033c4cc1cfa34.webm?t=1733692165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137740/extras/f02345333a681606799033c4cc1cfa34.mp4?t=1733692165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Sonar Scout》由来自五个不同国家的六位开发者共同制作，他们在位于瑞典的游戏开发者共享居住空间——Spelkollektivet相遇。我们非常希望您加入我们的Discord，分享您的反馈并与社区分享您最棒的游戏成绩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137740/extras/e7b9284488413d634c87b41e80ac854a.avif?t=1733692165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137740/extras_big/e7b9284488413d634c87b41e80ac854a.avif?t=1733692165 width=800 height=618 /></span></p>",
